---
title: cobre 👋
layout: base.liquid
---
<div class="space-y-2">
  <div class="row mt-8 mb-4">
    <h1>cobre
      <span class="wave">👋</span>
    </h1>
    {% comment %} <h1>
      <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cobredev/CV/main/CV.pdf" class="text-2xl">CV 📕</a>
    </h1> {% endcomment %}
  </div>
  <p>Just a guy with a passion for
    <strong>photography</strong>
    📸                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    and
    <strong>tech</strong>
    💻.</p><p> Check out my
    <a class="arrow-external" href="https://cobre.photos/">photography portfolio</a>.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2 space-y-8 w-full justify-between xl:flex-row xl:space-y-0 xl:gap-8 xl:space-x-8">
  {% comment %} <div class="shrink-0">
    <h2 class="text-zinc-400 mb-2 text-sm">Notes 📝</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2">
      {%- for note in site.notes -%}
        <div class="row">
          <a href="{{ note.url }}">{{ note.class }}</a>
          <p>{{ note.fsize }}</p>
        </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div> {% endcomment %}
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-zinc-400 mb-2 text-sm">Projects 🛠️</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2">
      {%- for project in collections.projects -%}
        <div>
          <div class="row">
            <a href="{{ project.url }}">{{ project.data.title }}</a>
            <small class="text-zinc-500">{{ project.data.dateLabel }}</small>
          </div>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 ">{{ project.data.description }}</p>
        </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-zinc-400 mb-2 text-sm">Extracurriculars 🎓</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2">
      {%- for extracurricular in collections.extracurriculars -%}
        <div>
          <div class="row">
            <a href="{{ extracurricular.url }}">{{ extracurricular.data.title }}</a>
            <small class="text-zinc-500">{{ extracurricular.data.dateLabel }}</small>
          </div>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">{{ extracurricular.data.description }}</p>
        </div>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div>
  <h2 class="mb-2">Contact 📫</h2>
  <p>You can email me at
    <a href="mailto:cobre@cobre.dev" class="underline-email arrow-external">cobre@cobre.dev</a>, or connect with me through my
    <a href="/links/">links</a>.
  </p>
</div>